 {
  "action": "type_string",
  "text": "; A hardware sprite the chips move for you, over a backdrop drawn once.\nBLITZ\n  ; build a shape, then turn it into hardware sprite 0\n  BitMap 2,16,16,2\n  Circle 8,8,7,1\n  Circle 8,8,4,2\n  GetaShape 0,0,0,16,16\n  GetaSprite 0,0\n\n  ; a backdrop, drawn ONCE - the loop never touches it again\n  BitMap 0,320,256,3\n  Cls 0\n  Boxf 0,170,319,255,2\n  Circle 230,70,40,3\n  Boxf 50,40,110,100,5\n\n  Slice 0,44,320,256,$fff8,3,8,8,320,320\n  Use Slice 0\n  Show 0\n\n  x.w=0\n  dx.w=2\n  While Joyb(0)=0\n    VWait\n    ShowSprite 0,x,72,0\n    x=x+dx\n    If x>304 Then dx=-dx\n    If x<0 Then dx=-dx\n  Wend\n"
 },
